reviewText: My wife is from Mexico and I guess this is kind of like their " I Love Lucy" or something. She was very happy with them.
Really is a great buy, great price and quality is great, the car charger is a nice addition, this company really make my day.

Previous to buy any product, I think is neccesary to know all its caracteristics. Conform with another web site the set contains three movies: Fuerte Audaz y Valiente, Tin Tan y las Modelos and Vagabundo y Millonario. I hope this information will be usefull. Also, I do not seen the movies but I rate these with 5 stars according to the actor.
Thanks.
